
<body class="common-structure">
    <header>
        <button id="returnToMenu" onclick="exitModule();"> <svg width="24" height="24"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd">
                <path
                    d="M12 11.293l10.293-10.293.707.707-10.293 10.293 10.293 10.293-.707.707-10.293-10.293-10.293 10.293-.707-.707 10.293-10.293-10.293-10.293.707-.707 10.293 10.293z" />
                </svg> </button>
        <div id="module-name">
            <h1>Ben's Story</h1>
            <h3>On Examination</h3>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="content module-slide">
        <p>Let's look at the case of Ben and a potential diagnosis of a congenital heart defect.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        {{#each preliminary_information}}
            {{list this}}
        {{/each}}
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <h1>Background History</h1>
        {{#each background_history}}
            {{list this}}
        {{/each}}
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <h1>On Examination</h1>
        {{#each on_examination}}
            {{ list this }}
        {{/each}}
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <p class="case-content">There is a radiology practice adjacent to your clinic and you organise a chest XR.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <p class="case-content"><img class="chest-xr" src={{xray}}></p>
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <h1>What are your differential diagnoses?</h1>
        <p class="case-content">Think carefully about your answer before you proceed to the next page.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content module-slide">
        <h1>What are your differential diagnoses?</h1>
        {{#each differential_diagnoses}}
           {{list this}}
        {{/each}}
    </section>
    
    <section class="content module-slide">
        <p class="case-content">Well done on examining your patient! Proceed to Interaction!</p>
    </section>



    <button id="previous" class="nav-button" onclick="nextSlide(-1)"> <svg width="24" height="24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd">
            <path d="M2.117 12l7.527 6.235-.644.765-9-7.521 9-7.479.645.764-7.529 6.236h21.884v1h-21.883z" /></svg>
    </button>
    <button id="next-module" class="text-button" onclick="nextModule();">Interaction</button>
    <button id="next" class="nav-button" onclick="nextSlide(1);"><svg width="24" height="24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd">
            <path d="M21.883 12l-7.527 6.235.644.765 9-7.521-9-7.479-.645.764 7.529 6.236h-21.884v1h21.883z" />
            </svg></button>
    <section id="navigation-tab">
        <a onclick="jumpSection('17040-oe.html', 'Case Examination');">Case Examination</a>
        <a onclick="jumpSection('17040-interaction.html', 'Interaction');">Interaction</a>
        <a onclick="jumpSection('17040-explanation.html', 'Explanation');">Explanation</a>
    </section>
</body>
